query:
INSERT INTO user_permissions (user_id, permission_id, effect, created_by)
                    SELECT $1, p.id, p.effect, $2
                    FROM unnest($3::BIGINT[], $4::TEXT[]) AS p(id, effect)
                    ON CONFLICT (user_id, permission_id) 
                    DO UPDATE SET 
                        effect = EXCLUDED.effect
